---
title: Logo in the Log In Form
description: Add logo to the [default log in system][link:../reference/extension/user] form.
...

Requires [user][link:../reference/extension/user] extension.

~~~ .css
.form-user::before {
  content: "";
  display: block;
  width: 80px;
  height: 80px;
  margin: 0 auto 1em;
  background: transparent url('./path/to/logo.png') no-repeat 50% 50%;
  background-size: 100% 100%;
}
~~~

Replace `./path/to/logo.png` with your logo image URL.